{"name":"Packhunt","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You choose to hunt alongside a trusted companion. During your daily preparations, you can choose an ally to serve as a companion. This ability counts as having an animal companion for the purposes of feat requirements and targeting (This includes using Command an Animal on them) and you can target your companion with focus spells that would normally target an animal companion. In addition, whenever you Hunt Prey, your companion also gains its benefits and gains an additional reaction that can only be used to Aid you when you @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.BlAOM2X92SI6HMtJ]{Seek}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.EA5vuSgJfiHH7plD]{Track}, or make an attack roll against your hunted prey.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Masterful Hunter Upgrade - Level 17</h3>\n<p>When you Hunt prey, your circumstance bonus to Perception checks when you Seek your prey is +4 and your circumstance bonus to Survival checks when you Track your prey is +4. You also ignore the penalty for making ranged attacks within your third range increment against the prey you're hunting.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-af9d9ad7-7fff-5e24-c047-28176fdb7c41\">Your companions also gain an additional reaction that can only be used to Aid you when you Seek, Track, or make an attack roll against your hunted prey.</span></p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"packhunt","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"traits":{"value":["ranger"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"classfeature","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","ownership":{"default":0,"XV70kTufyit7bW3z":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.jvrQms9qkYTKEvjy"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.310","createdTime":1703213156471,"modifiedTime":1703319754177,"lastModifiedBy":"XV70kTufyit7bW3z"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"Tflxs7gU6ivd338Q"}
